data.description: What a great location, walk to the St Augustine Beach and the Pier. Property backs to Ron Parker Field. A mature community with Grand Trees, Old Florida Home Styles, Close to everything. Come check out the Woodland neighborhood you will be glad you did. This 3 Bedroom 2 Bath Ranch style home has been re-plumbed and has a new Electric Breaker Box. Flood Zone X  Recent 4 Point and Wind Mid available. Make it your own! Includes a good size work/tool shed too.  Home is priced to sell.   Call for an appointment.
